node.text: Meet the Williams Collection → Combining classic mid-century elements, like tapered legs + solid mahogany, with modern craftsmanship like dovetail joinery + felt-lined drawers, these designs were made to last through moves, kids, and trends. Tap to shop.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by AllModern on August 19, 2021. May be an image of indoor and text that says 'G.BRAQUE'.

node.text: “Sew” much room for activities → Make space for productivity and hobbies with streamlined forms + functional accents that strike a work-life balance. Tap to shop.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by AllModern on August 19, 2021. May be an image of indoor.

node.text: Stone-cold style → Introduce impactful mixed materials with the warm wood + stone top of our Keri Vanity - oh and it comes in marble too. Tap to shop.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by AllModern on August 18, 2021. May be an image of furniture and indoor.

node.text: Living room | home office | dining room → Do it all in one space with the smooth curves + warm wood of our top-rated Sydnee Coffee Table. Did we mention there’s no assembly required? Tap to shop.
